    "body": "@cozz It's better to err on the safe side. If it happens that the cs_wallet lock is acquired before the cs_main lock it will result in a deadlock. \n\nI've added cs_main locks everywhere before that the cs_wallet lock is taken _except_ if I could clearly see within the function that the main lock is not necessary (for example, for address book manipulation).\n\n(This does make the issue visible that almost everything in the wallet code depends on the cs_main lock)\n",
